                <h1>About</h1>
                <hr>
                <p>Established in 1969 the institute was established to meet the needs of the masbateno especially in the technical and vocational field. Masbate being known as an agricultural province needed to have institutions that would usher in new
                    skills and knowledge that would create Masbate as a hub for innovative technology without having to forego its agricultural roots. With this in mind the founders of this institute sourced the pioneer faculty members from cebu with
                    the contract of providing ample housing allowances.</p>
            </div>

